data.title: Who wrote Genesis chapter 1? Was the person there?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 11): Who wrote Genesis chapter 1? Was the person there?

Good questions!! ;-)

The Bible attributes the first 5 books—also called the Pentateuch-the 5 volumes—to Moses. And NO!!! Moses was definitely not there.
